<p style="line-height:1.295;margin-bottom:8pt;margin-top:0pt;" dir="ltr"><span style="background-color:transparent;color:#000000;"><span style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">At Zeegna, we understand how important timely communication is when finding care or services. That’s why we prioritize connecting you with reliable, responsive providers to make your experience as seamless as possible.</span></span></p>
