<p style="line-height:1.295;margin-bottom:8pt;margin-top:0pt;" dir="ltr"><span style="background-color:transparent;color:#000000;"><span style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">To schedule a call or consultation, simply visit the provider’s profile and look for the scheduling option. You can select a time that works for you and connect directly with the provider. During this conversation, you can clarify details like the scope of services, availability, pricing, and how they approach meeting individual care needs.</span></span></p>
